We would like to avoid that and keep the variable. So the static block is used.
In the version 3.4.13 of zk we use, the packetLen also declares in this way.
public static final int packetLen;

  static {
    if (LOG.isDebugEnabled()) {
      LOG.debug("zookeeper.disableAutoWatchReset is " + disableAutoWatchReset);
    }

    packetLen = Integer.getInteger("jute.maxbuffer", 4194304);
  }

FYI, packetLen is removed in newer version of ZK.

